'''謝爾蓋·瓦列里耶維奇·阿克肖諾夫'''（{{lang-ru|Сергей Валерьевич Аксёнов}}；{{bd|1972年|11月26日}}）是前[[烏克蘭|烏克蘭]]的政治家及前[[克里米亞共和國|克里米亞]][[部長會議主席|部長會議主席]]（行政長官）<ref>{{cite news|title=Crimean Parliament Dismisses Cabinet and Sets Date for Autonomy Referendum|url=http://www.themoscowtimes.com/news/article/crimean-parliament-dismisses-cabinet-and-sets-date-for-autonomy-referendum/495391.html|accessdate=February 27, 2014|newspaper=[[The_Moscow_Times|The Moscow Times]]|date=February 27, 2014|archive-date=2018-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225110142/https://themoscowtimes.com/articles/crimean-parliament-dismisses-cabinet-and-sets-date-for-autonomy-referendum-32559|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年，被任命为現任[[克里米亚首脑|克里米亚首脑]]。

阿克肖諾夫在[[2014年克里米亞危機|2014年克里米亞危機]]中當[[克里米亞共和國|克里米亞部長會議]]（政府內閣）被[[攻城戰|包圍]]時被選出<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/02/28/world/europe/crimea-ukraine.html?hpw&rref=world&_r=0|title=Gunmen Seize Government Buildings in Crimea|publisher=The New York Times|date=2014-02-27|accessdate=2014-03-01|quote=Masked men with guns seized government buildings in the capital of Ukraine's Crimea region on Thursday, barricading themselves inside and raising the Russian flag after mysterious overnight raids that appeared to be the work of militant Russian nationalists who want this volatile Black Sea region ruled from Moscow.|archive-date=2014-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140303132928/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/02/28/world/europe/crimea-ukraine.html?hpw&rref=world&_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。3月初向俄羅斯尋求財政及軍事援助<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2014-03/01/c_126208445.htm|title=乌克兰克里米亚共和国总理期待俄给予财政援助|date=2014-03-01|accessdate=2014-04-05|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140422174045/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2014-03/01/c_126208445.htm|archivedate=2014-04-22}}</ref>，最終[[俄羅斯聯邦軍|俄羅斯聯邦軍]]派遣2萬2千大軍[[2014年克里米亞危機|進駐克里米亞]]。<ref>{{Cite news| url=http://news.163.com/14/0302/03/9MA5TUKP00014AED_all.html| title=克里米亚总理向普京求援 俄议会授权普京对乌动武（全文）| date=2014-03-02 03:22:10　| work=京华时报| location=北京| access-date=2014-04-02| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140318214713/http://news.163.com/14/0302/03/9MA5TUKP00014AED_all.html| archive-date=2014-03-18| dead-url=yes}}</ref>后在俄罗斯RT电视台专访中否认俄罗斯干涉克里米亚的说法，称克里米亚局势平静有序，还认为乌克兰新政府不是合法的，也不打算同他们合作。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2014-03/07/c_126236264.htm|title=克里米亚总理驳斥俄干涉说 称人民自主掌握命运|publisher=新华网国际|date=2014-03-07|accessdate=2014-04-05|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140422174047/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2014-03/07/c_126236264.htm|archivedate=2014-04-22}}</ref>3月18日，他与俄罗斯联邦总统普丁、塞瓦斯托波尔市市长[[阿列克谢·查利|阿列克谢·查利]]签署克里米亚入俄条约。<ref name="multiple">{{Cite web |url=http://news.sina.com.cn/w/2014-03-22/000329764803.shtml |title=克里米亚入俄法律程序完成 美俄掀“制裁大战” |accessdate=2014-04-02 |archive-date=2014-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140325195403/http://news.sina.com.cn/w/2014-03-22/000329764803.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>4月14日，阿克肖诺夫被普丁任命为俄联邦克里米亚共和国的临时行政长官，其任期直到举行选举。

